{
  "entries": [
    {
      "offset": "0xe9579",
      "back_en": "Wait, is she OK!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xe95db",
      "back_en": "...S-Such carelessness is... inexcusable...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Sotaque estilizado de Maroro preservado."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xe963f",
      "back_en": "...Oh, but I must put out the fire!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Sentido mantido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xe977f",
      "back_en": "She's no ordinary servant...!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xe991c",
      "back_en": "...S-Such carelessness... inexcusable...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Igual à anterior."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xe99bf",
      "back_en": "...I'll just... pretend I never saw any of that.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xeb983",
      "back_en": "Thank you so much... My body simply fails me",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xeb9b2",
      "back_en": "sometimes... and I have these sudden attacks...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xeba7c",
      "back_en": "Yes, it is only a short walk from here.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xebabe",
      "back_en": "No, I--I would dare not impose so on someone",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xebaed",
      "back_en": "Someone I have only just met, my distinguished lady...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Continua a frase; tom mantido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xebbdd",
      "back_en": "My apologies... I do not wish to be a burden,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xebc0d",
      "back_en": "but may I rely on you to see me safely home...?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Sentido mantido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xebc88",
      "back_en": "Whew... Thank you... Kind miss, may I know your",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Continua para o nome; ok."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xebce5",
      "back_en": "Atuy... Ah, such a wonderful name. There is",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xebd13",
      "back_en": "something so resonant to it... like a vast",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xebd4f",
      "back_en": "So kind... beautiful, and accepting of all",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xebd7c",
      "back_en": "like the mother ocean...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'things' omitido mas continua a frase."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xebe05",
      "back_en": "something like that... to me...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xebe46",
      "back_en": "That even in the renowned imperial capital,",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
