      "back_en": "madly.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xebf1c",
      "back_en": "Ah... Perhaps it was fate that made me fall",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Sentido mantido."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xebf4a",
      "back_en": "here... allowed me to meet you.",
