      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xecd1a",
      "back_en": "...I'd like you to elaborate a bit, I think.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xecd78",
      "back_en": "to do a census of the area.",
