      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xed73b",
      "back_en": "So, how'd it go, boss?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xed874",
      "back_en": "me again.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Exato."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0xed8d4",
      "back_en": "And of course, that one's no servant.",
